051b5d78916ee7389dfbd4e8871aab720415bd6e9ee0313dba770fc40ee7c68ac67d7918f2503458a3218e3bfc10691b5e379b65269106fde02c7e7a36eb7595  0003-update-ca-insert-newline-between-certs.patch"
